Package entity

Class Simu

java.lang.Object
entity.Simu
@Entity public class Simu extends Object
The Simu class represents a simulation in the system. It contains information about the simulation such as the time of the simulation, the number of customers, the number of service points, customer satisfaction, the number of reserved customers, and various average times and utilization rates for different desks in the simulation.
